        <h3><a href="https://darkplaces.bandcamp.com">bandcamp store</a></h3>
        
        <h1><a href="home.html">music from<br>dark places.</a></h1>

        <p>dark, exploratory music, set against a hopeful ambience. inspired in equal parts by the beauty and terror of the world around us.</p>

        <p>based in exeter, dark places was created as a hub for experimental and atmospheric music, with a focus on free distribution.</p>

        <h2>buying music from us.</h1>

        <p class="align-left">all releases can be acquired for free from our <a href="https://darkplaces.bandcamp.com">bandcamp page</a>. you can also find compact discs, cassettes and other limited merchandise there.</p>

        <p class="align-left">additionally, backup downloads of all releases are available in the archive below. if you use these downloads and want to donate to dark places, please feel free to purchase any work on bandcamp when you are able to.</p>

    </div>

</header>

